= RPI - Ruby Project Initializer

Initializes a full ruby project session.
(Just a small modification of visionmedia's commander-tool[1]).


== Features

* Creates directory structure
* Provides template files
* Git support


== Requirements

* visionmedia/commander (tested again v4.1.1)
  [1] https://github.com/visionmedia/commander/
* highline (tested again v1.6.11)
  [2] http://rubyforge.org/projects/highline/
